WEBVTT

00:09:29.250 --> 00:09:32.518
leaves you discouraged and anxious.

00:09:32.542 --> 00:09:35.559
You might even begin to see
how your own intensity and jealousy

00:09:35.583 --> 00:09:37.833
is causing problems
with colleagues at work.

00:09:39.208 --> 00:09:42.476
Understanding is
the first step to improving,

00:09:42.500 --> 00:09:45.559
and while you can't make
every unhealthy relationship healthy --

00:09:45.583 --> 00:09:47.684
some you're going
to have to leave behind --

00:09:47.708 --> 00:09:51.458
you can do your part every day
to do relationships better.

00:09:52.250 --> 00:09:53.893
And here's the exciting news:

00:09:53.917 --> 00:09:56.226
it's actually not rocket science.

00:09:56.250 --> 00:09:58.976
Open communication, mutual respect,

00:09:59.000 --> 00:10:01.226
kindness, patience --